<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eq.crgaming.com/viewarticle.asp?Article=4418">From Castersrealm Patch Archive:</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
PvP<br>
<br>
-Fixed a bug on Tallon and Vallon Zek that made player characters in non-human illusions immune to ranged attacks. <br>
-It is no longer possible for PC's to fear other PC's at all on any server. The same was also done for charm. <br>
-Pets can no longer be affected by charm spells. This should fix the issue that caused charm spells to make pets disappear. <br>
-NPCs who are pets of players and call for help from other NPCs will have their cries fall on deaf ears. <br>
